text: Nikolay Atanasov (born 20 May 1924) was a Bulgarian gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1924 births Category:Possibly living people Category:Bulgarian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Bulgaria Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:People from Botevgrad
